==Trivia==
*Laid down on the 2nd Nov 1938 she had a slow building process and was finally commissioned on 27th Feb '42.
*She was a very versatile ship, capable of carrying 25 planes, twelve midget submarines or 700 mines. In addition to being armed with with three dual 14cm/5.5" turrets, rivaling light cruisers in firepower. Lastly, she is also one of the fastest seaplane tenders within the IJN.
*After the losses at Midway she was primarily used as a fast transport, taking part in numerous Tokyo Express runs, just avoiding becoming involved in the Battle of Cape Esperance.
*After a refit and several more troop runs, she was engaged in a mission to Buin on the Solomon Island of Bougainville when she was attacked by numerous Dauntless and B-24s in July '43, her aviation fuel tanks were hit and she rapidly started to sink, with the loss of over 1000 men.

